				  <section>
					<h2>INNOVATION POLICY PLATFORM</h2>
				    <p class="fragment">Is a joint effort by the World Bank and the Organisation for Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD) to facilitate knowledge exchange and peer-to-peer learning on various policies specific to developed and developing countries by providing open data access through a rich knowledge discovery layer on top of a data warehouse of all OECD and World Bank data, aimed at transform available data into strategic intelligence.</p>
				  </section>
				  <section>
